Heartbeat
---------

Simple sign of life test for RTAI. Creates a task with priority 99 that
will drive a running light on an attached standard PC keyboard. Requires
RTAI with RTDM support.

WARNING: This tool can cause high latencies (several ms). Use only for
debugging, not on production systems!

To use:
make
./run

Jan Kiszka - jan.kiszka@web.de

*******************************************************************************

Semtest
-------

Tests all RTDM sem operations.

To use:
make
./runs

Mutextest
-------

Tests all RTDM mutex operations.

To use:
make
./runm

Paolo
